<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Castle Attack - The Proving Grounds</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/provinggrounds/css/terminal.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="terminal">
        <div class="ascii-box">
<pre>
===============================================
          ATTACK THE CASTLE
   "Storm the fortress for treasure!"
===============================================
</pre>
        </div>

        <p>The castle looms before you, its dark towers reaching into the sky.
        Within its walls lie 19 rooms filled with monsters, traps, and treasure.</p>

        <div class="stats" style="margin: 20px 0;">
            <div class="stat">
                <span class="stat-label">HP:</span>
                <span class="stat-value"><%= user.hp %>/<%= user.max_hp %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
                <span class="stat-label">Power:</span>
                <span class="stat-value"><%= user.power %>/<%= user.max_power %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
                <span class="stat-label">Current Room:</span>
                <span class="stat-value"><%= typeof currentRoom !== 'undefined' ? currentRoom : 'Entrance' %></span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="menu" style="margin-top: 20px;">
            <div class="menu-item">
                <span class="menu-key">A)</span>
                <form action="/combat/castle/attack" method="POST" style="display: inline;">
                    <button type="submit">Storm the Castle</button>
                </form>
            </div>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <span class="menu-key">&lt;</span>
                <a href="/combat">Return to Combat Menu</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="status-bar">
            <span>[<%= user.name %>]</span>
            <span>Level: <%= user.level %></span>
            <span>Gold: <%= user.gold %></span>
            <span>HP: <%= user.hp %>/<%= user.max_hp %></span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="/provinggrounds/js/terminal.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
